WEBVTT

00:12:59.876 --> 00:13:02.097
that would, at the very least,
make you sick --

00:13:02.121 --> 00:13:04.479
I can just about understand
why someone would say,

00:13:04.503 --> 00:13:07.209
"This can't be right,
let's wait, let's slow down,

00:13:07.233 --> 00:13:09.553
maybe we aren't understanding
this the full way,

00:13:09.577 --> 00:13:10.839
maybe it will go away."

00:13:10.863 --> 00:13:12.847
Can you understand why that might happen?

00:13:12.871 --> 00:13:16.234
RM: Definitely! What I asked them to do
was to do that investigation --

00:13:16.258 --> 00:13:18.191
which apparently, they did do.

00:13:18.704 --> 00:13:21.268
By the summer of 2017,

00:13:21.292 --> 00:13:23.950
they for sure knew
the dimensions of the problem.

00:13:23.974 --> 00:13:28.307
And they still tried
to brazen their way through it.

00:13:28.331 --> 00:13:30.450
And my simple point to them was,